## Cwiczenia

@1577541974636
q: Mili (m) * Mikro (µ)
a: Nano (n) (10^-3 * 10^-6 = 10^-9)

@1577541974736
q: Mili (m) * Nano (n)
a: Piko (p) (10^-3 * 10^-9 = 10^-12)

@1577541974836
q: 1 / (Mili (m))
a: Kilo (k) (1 / 10^-3 = 10^3)

